<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>酷安话题-NAS</title><link>https://www.coolapk.com/</link><atom:link href="http://10.0.0.5:1200/coolapk/huati/NAS" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>酷安话题-NAS - Powered by RSSHub</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>contact@rsshub.app (RSSHub)</webMaster><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 05:05:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>5</ttl><item><title>【今天发现连接不上套件中心了】#黑群晖# 昨天升级了一下系统，今天发现连接不上套件中心了，大家的可以连接上吗？是系统问题？</title><description>&lt;p&gt;【今天发现连接不上套件中心了】&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E9%BB%91%E7%BE%A4%E6%99%96?type=12&quot;&gt;#黑群晖#&lt;/a&gt; 昨天升级了一下系统，今天发现连接不上套件中心了，大家的可以连接上吗？是系统问题？&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70856793</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70856793</guid><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 04:38:11 GMT</pubDate><author>baodao5</author></item><item><title>江苏联通，说我上传过多被限速了，v6也掉了[流汗滑稽][流汗滑稽]联通师傅现在在我家“搜查ing”[流汗滑稽]#NAS# #路由器# #电脑玩家#</title><description>&lt;p&gt;江苏联通，说我上传过多被限速了，v6也掉了[流汗滑稽][流汗滑稽]联通师傅现在在我家“搜查ing”[流汗滑稽]&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/NAS?type=0&quot;&gt;#NAS#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%99%A8?type=0&quot;&gt;#路由器#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6?type=0&quot;&gt;#电脑玩家#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/8e8d377249a575b8710cc9f8e8ed7c13.png&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/1f4489a829fcf861aab7dfc422891fba.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/1624b085fde311dcff3db015fd3b0329.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/28ae9b82c9548201ccb1a9436af3b953.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70853837</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70853837</guid><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 01:38:01 GMT</pubDate><author>翔之广宇</author></item><item><title>江苏联通，说我上传过多被限速了，v6也掉了[流汗滑稽][流汗滑稽][流汗滑稽]#NAS# #路由器# #电脑玩家#</title><description>&lt;p&gt;江苏联通，说我上传过多被限速了，v6也掉了[流汗滑稽][流汗滑稽][流汗滑稽]&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/NAS?type=0&quot;&gt;#NAS#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%99%A8?type=0&quot;&gt;#路由器#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6?type=0&quot;&gt;#电脑玩家#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/f0d007922e4b1e2741015deb0df82f26.png&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/14b9d0b3d119016ca59dcac8caaf0901.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70853547</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70853547</guid><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 01:18:29 GMT</pubDate><author>翔之广宇</author></item><item><title>#Emby# 搞了个服，有没有要加入的，不免</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/Emby?type=0&quot;&gt;#Emby#&lt;/a&gt;  搞了个服，有没有要加入的，不免&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/98229dcc49eb6a1c82024afff4f431b0.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/71e275930560796c8cf1ae85af44baf2.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70848518</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70848518</guid><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 14:00:49 GMT</pubDate><author>要不要买菜_099</author></item><item><title>#NAS# 预出一台nas配置如下i3 4150+华硕b85主板，8g ddr3 1333hz内存有一个64g固态sata系统盘，还有四块500g机械硬盘，全套出售，现在装的飞牛，平时在家里吃灰...</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/NAS?type=0&quot;&gt;